        dev.off()
                    </pre>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td class="labkey-form-label">fileout:&lt;name&gt;</td>
                    <td>A file output that can be downloaded LabKey Server, and may be of any file type.  For example, use <code>fileout</code>
